p Runs the 'ping' test within the simulator (simulation times valid for 32bits architectures)

$ $SG_TEST_EXENV ./ping_simulator${EXEEXT:=} ${srcdir:=.}/../../msg/small_platform.xml ${srcdir:=.}/ping.xml $ARGS
